Value: Donaco International Limited engages in the leisure and entertainment business in the Asia Pacific region. It operates Star Vegas Resort & Club, a casino and hotel complex comprising approximately 100 gaming tables, 800 slot machines, and 385 hotel rooms in Poipet, Cambodia; and Aristo International Hotel, a boutique casino that comprises 400 hotel rooms in northern Vietnam located in Yunnan, China. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
